  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Bombard Weapons are used to exterminate the population =
of
  an enemy colony, and to damage the planet itself, lowering its quality.<o=
:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Higher technology levels enable bombard weapons to wield
  greater levels of destruction.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Bombarding populated colonies is widely considered to be
  barbaric, and engaging in bombardment will negatively affect your reputat=
ion
  with other empires. However if the target of the bombardment has a poor
  reputation (due to their own notorious actions) then other empires will be
  less concerned.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
